@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="home-page">
	<section class="home-intro">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">SocialLife</p>
			<h1>Stay connected with friends and trends</h1>
			<p class="intro-text">See what your network is sharing, discover new connections, and explore the moments that matter.</p>
		</div>
		<button class="btn btn-primary">Create new post</button>
	</section>

	<div class="home-layout">
		<main class="feed-column">
			<div class="feed-header">
				<h2>News Feed</h2>
				<span>Latest updates from your community</span>
			</div>

			<article class="feed-card">
				<div class="feed-card-meta">
					<div>
						<h3>Elena Rivera</h3>
						<p>2h ago · Product Design</p>
					</div>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Follow</button>
				</div>
				<p>Just wrapped up a team brainstorm on our next campaign. Grateful for the momentum and new ideas!</p>
				<div class="feed-card-actions">
					<button class="btn btn-link">Like</button>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Comment</button>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Share</button>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="feed-card">
				<div class="feed-card-meta">
					<div>
						<h3>Marcus Chen</h3>
						<p>5h ago · Software Engineering</p>
					</div>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Follow</button>
				</div>
				<p>Exploring new ways to streamline team collaboration across projects. Any recommendations for remote-friendly tooling?</p>
				<div class="feed-card-actions">
					<button class="btn btn-link">Like</button>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Comment</button>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Share</button>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="feed-card">
				<div class="feed-card-meta">
					<div>
						<h3>Sofia Patel</h3>
						<p>Yesterday · Content Strategy</p>
					</div>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Follow</button>
				</div>
				<p>New blog post is live: balancing creativity and consistency when building your personal brand online.</p>
				<div class="feed-card-actions">
					<button class="btn btn-link">Like</button>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Comment</button>
					<button class="btn btn-link">Share</button>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>

		<aside class="recommendations-column">
			<div class="sidebar-panel">
				<div class="sidebar-title">
					<h2>Recommended connections</h2>
					<span>Expand your network</span>
				</div>
				<ul class="recommendation-list">
					<li>
						<div>
							<strong>Amara Johnson</strong>
							<p>Marketing • 8 mutual friends</p>
						</div>
						<button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Connect</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<div>
							<strong>Noah Williams</strong>
							<p>Engineering • 5 mutual friends</p>
						</div>
						<button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Connect</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<div>
							<strong>Jade Torres</strong>
							<p>Product • 12 mutual friends</p>
						</div>
						<button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Connect</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="sidebar-panel sidebar-secondary">
				<h3>Quick tips</h3>
				<p>Share a status update, congratulate a connection, or join a group to keep your profile active and visible.</p>
			</div>
		</aside>
	</div>
</div>
